snippet.title: DemonriftTD first gameplay video
snippet.description:
Hello everyone, 

After a very long while we're finally posting the first ever gameplay video of demonrift td here. After all these years, believe it or not development is still going on :). We are hoping to into beta testing phase very soon... 

So hopefully with this video you guys can get a glimpse of what this game is actually all about..... enjoy and stay tuned for incoming videos about the game....
